---
import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---


<BaseLayout title="About | Ronald Baruelo" description="About Ronald Baruelo - Technical Support and Web Developer">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/wokandcode.png"
					alt="Ronald Baruelo at work with a colleague"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						I have a strong passion for technology and its power to solve problems and create great
						experiences. My journey began with a solid academic foundation, earning both a
						Bachelor's in Information Technology and a Diploma in Cloud Engineering. This
						education gave me a comprehensive understanding of the digital world, from the
						fundamentals of development to the complexities of modern cloud infrastructure.
					</p>
					<p>
						Throughout my career, I've developed a versatile skill set focused on building and
						maintaining robust technical systems. My core expertise lies in Technical Support,
						Web Development, Databases, and a wide range of Cloud skills. I enjoy the process
						of turning complex challenges into simple, elegant solutions that not only work
						efficiently but also bring a positive impact. Ultimately, I believe technology
						should make people's lives better. My goal is to use my skills to build and
						support systems that are not just powerful, but also intuitive and genuinely
						helpful.
					</p>
					<p>
						You can view my work at my <a href="https://github.com/ronaldbaruelo">GitHub profile</a>.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Graduate Diploma on Data Analytics</p>
					<p>Diploma on Cloud Engineer and Bachelor on Information Technology.</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Technical Support , Web dev ,Databases, cloud skills and Data Analytics</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content p {
		margin-bottom: 2em;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
